Text-UTX-Simple version 0.02_00


INSTALLATION

To install this library, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build,
you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


